{"tid":401723,"cid":15,"subCid":0,"title":"賭冧市輸到執笠！大鱷仍「死撐」：是市場錯 (00:15)","createTime":"2017-09-16T00:16:10.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-16T10:39:00.000Z","uid":17738,"like":3,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"36b5f18a0c7fcfb42f7c7ceb564deabc5d452842","tid":401723,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:16:10.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170916/img/20170916001502fi_p1.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170916%2Fimg%2F20170916001502fi_p1.jpg&h=b711d354&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n【<a href=\"http://on.cc\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fon.cc&d=PwBGKwisCUV%2FBu%2FFbY7d76WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=756317ac\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">on.cc</a>東網專訊】今年全球股市愈唱淡愈上升，再有「大鱷」要低頭了！據外國傳媒報道，傳奇基金經理、2008年金融危機期間沽空銀行股而聞名的對沖基金Eclectica Asset Management團隊首領Hugh Hendry，其基金在連蝕兩年後，最終要黯然離場。<br />\n<br />\n資料顯示，Eclectica在2016年虧損4%，今年首8個月更勁蝕9.4%，現時基金僅餘3,000萬美元，要倒閉了。不過，Hendry至今仍「死撐」，不是他的錯，而是市場出錯！<br />\n<br />\n他說：「事情本來不應是這樣，尤其是今年夏天全球經濟向好，出現了史上第一次全球所有經濟體同時增長，不知道這樣的局面會維持多久......現在我們面對非常怪異的環境，雖然知道金融資產泡沫被谷大，但美國看起來不會有危機、中國經濟持續增長、歐洲經濟也在復甦，風險資產升勢不會改變......」<br />\n<br />\n回顧Hendry在2016年3月警告，如果中國將人民幣貶值20%，全球立即玩完！在2016年11月警告，英國脫歐噩夢僅開始，2017年歐盟恐要瓦解。<br />\n<br />\nHendry於Eclectica資產管理工作15年，即使在2008年金融海嘯期間，他仍獲得正回報達30%，如今要投降了。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170916/20170916001502fi.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fm.on.cc%2Fnc%2Ffin%2F20170916%2F20170916001502fi.html&d=PwBGKwisCUV%2FBu%2FFbY7d76WGW%2FHqnCni%2B1xW1zXhD2s%3D&h=70eb5d5d\" target=\"_blank\">http://m.on.cc/nc/fin/20170916/20170916001502fi.html</a>"},{"pid":"84e4ba828b621067e423852f7450b80b75c10e92","tid":401723,"uid":33263,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:33:06.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"4ba7ac3a75239d6b19cb143ea531c974cb9cc930","tid":401723,"uid":72825,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:49:19.000Z","msg":"大c<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/cry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"77d78700c25e182fd17a7c56e1fda12542ccc043","tid":401723,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T00:52:19.000Z","msg":"基金鬼佬中嘅沈大師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"507bc332b2575a29cc55da639a748820b4c5eb64","tid":401723,"uid":40397,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T01:37:42.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基金鬼佬中嘅沈大師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n沈大師叻d，佢鳩嗡但可能反手操作我地唔知<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/hehe.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"ad3a5a81f6706966092404812716093d17c10377","tid":401723,"uid":54870,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:08:11.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://holland.pk/2wqzu7yr\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fholland.pk%2F2wqzu7yr&h=d8e61634&s={SIZE}\" />"},{"pid":"d8196902b463072aaccd0244f98a5b3dca50a8b0","tid":401723,"uid":5537,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:13:46.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>基金鬼佬中嘅沈大師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪佢d 結拜兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e1de8e8deb66d0d54e87b25994fbb581f0ed61ad","tid":401723,"uid":17738,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-16T02:15:21.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>基金鬼佬中嘅沈大師 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n係咪佢d 結拜兄弟<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n大家都係「機構投資人」 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal